Hi Rod,

The T&Cs for the Merchant Processing Agreement are required for all accounts for CardConnect and First Data.
I assume both CardConnect Direct and Shift4 are submitting the merchant applications via the same platform-
Via Advantage.

There are limited scenarios whereby First Data will board a merchant to CardConnect without an application; it would
require CardConnect to have the proper documentation, which is captured via the application or attestation form.
For example, for merchants who apply via an approved and integrated partner system (like a POS system), they have an
attestation form that they complete that collects the required information. We do see this a lot for IS Vs.

I look forward to hearing from you. Have a good evening!
